commit 6c9a99e5f7e1bc065ba55cbe26510e34b7699784
Author: René Bertin <rjvbertin@gmail.com>
Date:   Fri Feb 20 16:47:38 2026 +0100

    Minimal port to Darwin/Mac
    
    This makes an almost-standalone bundle of the application, but it will depend
    
    - on the Qt libraries installed in a central location as
      they are not embedded in the app bundle
    - on DBus and the kdiskmark_helper application that must be
      installed in a pre-determined location. This could be inside
      the app bundle, but the DBus service definition file has to
      be installed in a dedicated, system-central location, so
      for now we install the helper in the same location as on Linux.
    
    Committed from host : Bola

